  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "Maverick Silens 2 Profile is the quietest LED moving head ever released for theatre and studio applications. This innovative 560W moving head is completely fanless and designed to operate in total silence without compromises in color-consistency and output. The unit features a 10,000+ lumen output, customized optics with variable CMY + CTO color mixing for superior, luscious colors and a +/- green adjustment to ensure perfectly rendered skin tones. Maverick Silens is also capable of superb animation effects via 1 rotating, 1 static gobo wheel, 1 prism, fully variable frost and an emulated red shift for a tungsten punch. Control your way with DMX, sACN, Art-Net, or CRMX.",
